<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Time-sensitive funding</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #f7f7f7; margin: 0; padding: 24px; color: #111827;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0;">
        {{ contact_name or "Hi there" }},
      </p>
      {% if custom_body_html %}
      {{ custom_body_html | safe }}
      {% else %}
      <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We reviewed {{ company or "your account" }} and saw recent deposits near {{ avg_deposits | default('your latest levels') }}.
        {% if nsf_count is not none %}
        NSFs are holding at {{ nsf_count }}, which signals we should lock in a working-capital cushion before the next cycle.
        {% endif %}
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        {{ business_name }} can priority-queue a tailored offer today so you have funds in place before any gap impacts operations. The underwriting window for this tranche closes shortly, so a quick reply keeps your file at the front of the line.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Reply with "send details" or propose a 10-minute time today and I'll send the numbers immediately.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0;">
        Regards,<br />
        {{ from_name }}<br />
        {{ business_name }}
      </p>
      {% endif %}
      <footer style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding-top: 16px;">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;">{{ business_name }} â€¢ {{ business_address }}</p>
        <p style="margin: 0;">Opt out of future updates anytime <a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}" style="color: #dc2626;">here</a>.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
